metadata.name: Jungle Warriors
metadata.description:
Billion and billions of years ago, with no existence of the human race on planet Earth, it was a serene place where all the natural creatures peacefully coexisted!
And then enters mankind as we know it. Though we haven’t been kind to Mother Nature since then, we now have to face her wrath.

Lo and behold, the protectors of the jungle’s spirit, the jungle warriors, are here to get all that is theirs and are ready to rule the world together. They carry life and death on their shoulders and are on a mission to find peace by creating a new life for all.
